AmVestors Financial Corp said itdeclared a 25 pct stock dividend payable June 19 to holders ofrecord June one, subject to an increase in authorized shares.    It said shareholders will vote at the April 23 annualmeeting to increase authorized shares to 25 mln from 10 mln.    The company also said it plans to pay an initial quarterlydividend of five cts a share on the shares. Reuter&#3;